## PHASE 8: Frontend — Add / Edit Job Post (/recruiter/jobs/new)
[ ] Multi-step form wizard:
    [ ] Step 1 — Job Basics:
        [ ] Job Title (text, required)
        [ ] Job Type (dropdown: Full-time, Part-time, Contract, Internship, Remote)
        [ ] Experience Level (dropdown)
        [ ] Number of Openings (number)
        [ ] Application Deadline (date picker, must be future date)
    [ ] Step 2 — Job Details:
        [ ] Job Description (rich text editor: bold, italic, bullet points)
        [ ] Required Skills (multi-tag input with search/autocomplete)
        [ ] Nice-to-Have Skills (multi-tag input)
    [ ] Step 3 — Compensation & Location:
        [ ] Location (text or "Remote" checkbox)
        [ ] Salary Range (min-max slider with toggle for "Don't disclose salary")
    [ ] Step 4 — Review & Publish:
        [ ] Preview card of the job post (as candidates will see it)
        [ ] "Save as Draft" button
        [ ] "Publish Now" button
[ ] Progress indicator showing current step (1/4, 2/4...)
[ ] "Back" and "Next" buttons with step validation
[ ] Auto-save draft on step navigation

## PHASE 9: Frontend — Applicant Pipeline (/recruiter/jobs/:id/applicants)
