    [ ] Sort: Highest Match Score | Newest First | Name A-Z
[ ] Applicants table/kanban view (toggle button):
    [ ] Table view columns: Rank, Candidate Name, Match Score, Skills Match, Status, Applied On, Actions
    [ ] Match Score shown as colored progress bar (red < 50%, orange 50-70%, green > 70%)
    [ ] Actions per row: View Profile | Shortlist | Reject | Add Note
[ ] Bulk action bar (appears on checkbox selection):
    [ ] "Shortlist Selected" button
    [ ] "Reject Selected" button
[ ] Candidate Detail Drawer/Modal (on row click):
    [ ] Candidate avatar, name, headline, contact
    [ ] AI Match Score breakdown:
        [ ] Skills matched (green chips)
        [ ] Skills missing (red chips)
        [ ] Overall score progress bar
    [ ] Resume preview/download button
    [ ] Work experience timeline
    [ ] Education list
    [ ] Status change dropdown (with save button)
    [ ] Notes section (add/view recruiter notes)
    [ ] Application status history timeline

## PHASE 10: Frontend — Shortlisted Candidates (/recruiter/shortlisted)
