## PHASE 11: Frontend — Recruiter Settings (/recruiter/settings)
[ ] Company Profile form:
    [ ] Company name, logo upload, description, industry, size, website
[ ] Account settings:
    [ ] Change email
    [ ] Change password
    [ ] Notification preferences (new application alerts, daily digest)

## DELIVERABLES / ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA
[ ] Recruiter can create, edit, publish, and close job posts
[ ] Multi-step job form validates each step before proceeding
[ ] Applicants are listed and sortable by AI match score
[ ] Recruiter can filter applicants by status stage
[ ] Recruiter can shortlist/reject individual or bulk candidates
[ ] Status changes trigger email notifications to candidates
[ ] Shortlisted candidates are aggregated across all jobs
[ ] All recruiter pages are responsive on mobile/tablet
